This creates a subtle pulsing glow effect using `box-shadow` that expands from 0 to 4px and fades out. The color `rgb(16 185 129)` is emerald-500, matching the active health dot color. The animation runs continuously at 2s intervals with `ease-in-out` for a calm, non-distracting pulse.

